		</li>
		<li>
			This will open the 'New Sample Set' page. The following fields are to be completed:
			  <ul>
			  	<li>
			  		Facility - Choose the Facility at which you will be sampling from the dropdown menu (Tip: You can begin typing the name of the facility to narrow down the list of available options). A full list of 
			  		available Facilities as well as their details can be found by clicking on the 'View Resources' menu on the top right menu bar and then selecting 'Facilities'. If the Facility that you require is not 
			  		in the list use the 'Contact' link (on the bottom of the page) to get in touch. 
			  		<%= image_tag("help_pages/resources_dropdown.jpeg", :alt => "sample set new page", :class=>"center_border_img") %>
			  	</li>
			  	<li>
			  		Project - State which Project the samples will be collected for. Again, a full list of projects available can be found under the Resources menu.
			  	</li>
			  	<li>
			  		Sampling Date - Choose which date you would like to carry out the actual sampling on. 
			  	</li>
