			  		Sampling Date - Choose which date you would like to carry out the actual sampling on. 
			  	</li>
			  </ul>
			<%= image_tag("help_pages/ss_new.jpeg", :alt => "sample set new page", :class=>"center_border_img") %>
		</li>
